    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2006 BMW M3 represents a superlative example of the E46 chassis, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine with its signature high-pressure individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, this unit has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe. The factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional power delivery out of corners, while the suspension retains its original damping characteristics with zero bushing deflection. Finished in a concours-level exterior with a perfectly preserved interior, this vehicle offers an analog driving experience that is increasingly rare. Every component, from the VANOS system to the hydraulic actuators, has been vetted for peak performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
